    • Inventory & Restocking Management

    Returned items are automatically evaluated and added back to your available inventory with just a few clicks, reducing downtime and manual entry errors.

    Custom Condition
    Settings & Product Detailing

    Set Custom Conditions

    Assess the item's condition, market demand, and your pricing history to apply the optimal discount automatically.

    Detailed Descriptions

    Craft unique descriptions for each returned item. Highlight any imperfections or the 'as-new' status, ensuring transparency and setting the right expectations for buyers.

    Image Uploads

    Showcase the actual condition of the product with high-quality images. Upload multiple photos from different angles, providing a visual assurance that builds trust with potential buyers.

    Condition-Based Pricing

    Link your custom conditions directly to pricing rules. Automatically adjust the price based on the condition set, ensuring fair pricing for both you and your customers.
